      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Chop your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly dice</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing it with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-55-copy-1724339523881-x200.jpg",
